reviews.title: Great new wine bar
reviews.text: A great new wine bar, with very friendly and knowledgeable staff.  Love the concept - so many wines and a great diverse selection; choose either a taste, a half glass or more and then move on to the next!  Opportunity to have good snacks or a nice meal depending on your mood, all in a relaxed environment.  We had a fun night!

mgmtResponse.text:
Hello Rhysj999, Thank you very much for visiting and leaving this very first 5 bubble review for our newly opened Wine Bar in the heart of The Hague's Zeeheldenkwartier. With over 100 wines to discover by our self exploring wine experience. You can serve yourself a small taster, a medium glass or a regular glass of wine. Served with great food coming from our late night kitchen. 

Proud and happy that you have enjoyed the experience and we are looking forward to welcoming  you back with us in the foreseeable future.

Warm regards,
Team The Hague Social Club
